==English==

===Etymology===
From [[home]] + [[page]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# the main or first page of a [[Web site]], typically with [[hyperlink]]s to the other pages
# the page set to open in a [[Web browser]] when it is [[load]]ed
# the Web page which one first visits in any [[hypertext]] system or set of hyperlinked documents

====Alternative spellings====
* home page

